column5: Edit the highlighted "Drop down Menus" to your currently still open Dungeons, to find your easily achieveable Levels at the end of your DP!

The recommended "To" values after clicking the RESET BUTTON are set with a Battle Mage with normal Mine and no heavy shrooming as a base value, so you can add a few levels on top if you are a heavy shroomer or have a strong PvE Class.                                  With the new Item Quality rework even more is possible to clear, benchmark will get updated after further testing.
